high_descs: Turn around and go to the other side of the counter with the sink.
Pick up the mango with the popsicle stick in it.
Go to the end of the counter next to the sink between the sink and the wall.
Put the mango in the sink, turn the water on, turn it off, and take the mango out.
Turn and go to the fridge.
Put the mango in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Rinse off the round Mango with the popsicle stick in it and put it in the Fridge.

high_descs: Walk to the other side of the sink.
Pick up the yellow mango from the counter.
Walk to the larger sink at the end of the counter.
Put the mango in the sink to rinse and take it out.
Turn right to reach the fridge.
Put the mango on the top shelf of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed Mango in the Fridge.

high_descs: Walk to the opposite side of the sink.
Grab the mango that is sitting next to the sink.
Take mango to side of the sink, place inside.
Wash the mango off by turning on faucet.
Take the mango to the fridge.
Place the mango inside the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Get the mango from the side of the sink, place inside wash, then place mango inside fridge.
